Use our special wine label

00:20:08.240 --> 00:20:10.020
to pass the word to Ding Yi.

00:20:22.920 --> 00:20:23.330
Ding Yi.

00:20:24.040 --> 00:20:25.050
The exact spot of the photo

00:20:25.440 --> 00:20:27.180
is written on the back
of the wine label.

